title: ICalloutVariable.VariableName
description: Gets the name of the hole callout variable as it appears in the Dimension PropertyManager page in the Dimension Text box.
returns: Name of the hole callout variable as it appears in the Dimension PropertyManager page in the Dimension Text box
remarks:
Call
ICalloutVariable::UserReadableVariableName
to get the name of the hole callout variable as it appears in the Dimension PropertyManager page in the
Callout value
drop-down list box.
